{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"巴拿马，响起一声春雷！","authors":["周纲"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":1,"day":16}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，响起一声春雷！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周纲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一声春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在何处响起？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"英雄的加勒比，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒涛不息！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大西洋和太平洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨臂高高举起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马人民反抗的大旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"约翰逊的国情咨文，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"墨迹渗着血迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街的谎言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"屠刀加上弹皮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马，血的河流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲毁了骗人的梦呓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撕开了强盗的画皮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从六十年的屈辱里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"认识了仇敌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从催泪瓦斯的迷烟里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看清了吃人的美帝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是谁的土地？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么？巴拿马人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掬饮自己的河水，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要向华尔街的大亨纳税；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么？巴拿马人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能看见祖国的天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飘扬着自己的国旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的路不能走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的家不能息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己的天空河流和土地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不能自由地歌唱和呼吸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的强权，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枪杀了协议；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的铁丝网，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"囚禁了公理；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的皮靴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踩着巴拿马的尊严，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的刺刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑着巴拿马的独立！……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！巴拿马、血的巴拿马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六十年了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我夜夜听见你在呐喊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我夜夜听见你在哭泣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然你能挽住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大西洋和太平洋的狂涛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"既然你能容汇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大西洋和太平洋的雷雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为什么？为什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不举起你铁的拳头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粉碎身上的镣铐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲涮心上的屈辱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夺回民族的尊严！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打倒你的仇敌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是漫长的忍耐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聚集了仇恨的旋风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是如山的苦难，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆发了白热的岩浆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冲天的火炬！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死亡的河岸复活了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从中美洲昂首站立。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"血的浪头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炸响了第一声春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十个人倒下去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个巴拿马一齐站起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整个巴拿马一齐站起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亚洲，非洲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉丁美洲……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"漫天沉雷吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍地风云急！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马呀，我们支援你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马呀，我们捍卫你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的仇敌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也是我们的仇敌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的血迹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是我们的血迹！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，全世界受美国侵略，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干涉、控制的国家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一同联合起；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗！反抗！冲击！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来呀，受苦受难的兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起来呀，饥寒交迫的奴隶！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即使是拳头对刺刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"石头迎弹雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们也要——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反抗到底！战斗到底！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纸糊的老虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只会吓倒胆小鬼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讹诈的核弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能叫变节者屈膝！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上，只有人民的力量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才不可抗拒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世界上，只有人民的团结，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才真正无与匹敌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听呵，巴拿马的怒吼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经响彻大地！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听呵，解放斗争的春雷，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已经震撼天宇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华尔街的摩天高楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便是绝好的绞架，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怒涛滚滚的大西洋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便是绝好的坟地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴拿马人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全世界人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快快拉紧绞索，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用力！用力！用力！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天伟大的预言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便是明天辉煌的胜利——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“要扫除一切害人虫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"全无敌。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四·一·十四"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}